title: Why Your Perfectionism is Destroying Your Productivity
itunes:title: Why Your Perfectionism is Destroying Your Productivity
description:
You can be a perfectionist or you can be productive, but you can't be both. In this episode, I am going to talk to you about how to get rid of your perfectionism so that you can be more productive.
